WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
The dog 犬 一人称 単数の代名詞

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:10.000
I, my, me, mine その用例

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:19.000
I am a dog. I have a master. My master is very kind to me. He takes me everywhere he goes.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Mine is the best of masters.

